    <article id="post-9600" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/9600.html" rel="bookmark">[Laravel 5.7 文档] 官方扩展包 —— 第三方登录解决方案：Laravel Socialite</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-09-09T10:43:02+08:00">2018-09-09</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-09-09T10:43:01+08:00">2018-09-09 10:43:01</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/nonfu">
                            学院君
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    1982 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/9600.html#comments">
                        3 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9600.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/238fef4c23a91ecfa0ec407751adacb6-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9600.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/238fef4c23a91ecfa0ec407751adacb6-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>简介
除了传统的基于表单的登录认证外，Laravel 还可以通过 Laravel Socialite 提供 OAuth 认证，目前支持的认证驱动包括 Facebook、Twitter、Google、LinkedIn、GitHub 和 Bitbucket。

注：其他平台的驱动可以在社区驱的 Socialite 提供者网站上找到。

安装
要使用 Socialite，首先需要通过 Comp...</p>
        </div>

