                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/9554.html#comments">
                        2 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9554.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/6f963ff1b56998436cba0acf33ab7b8b-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9554.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/6f963ff1b56998436cba0acf33ab7b8b-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>简介

注：想要快速上手？只需要在新安装的 Laravel 应用下运行 php artisan make:auth 和 php artisan migrate，这两个命令会生成用户登录注册所需要的所有东西，然后在浏览器中访问 http://your-app.test/register 即可。

Laravel 中实现登录认证非常简单。实际上，几乎所有东西 Laravel 都已经为你配置好...</p>
        </div>

