    <article id="post-9469" class="kb-article-excerpt post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail">
        <header class="entry-header page-header">
            <h2 class="entry-title">
                <a href="../post/9469.html" rel="bookmark">关于 jwt 的一些分享</a>
            </h2>

            <div class="entry-meta text-muted">
                <span class="posted-on">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i> Posted on
                    <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2018-06-01T11:03:15+08:00">2018-06-01</time>
                    <time class="updated" datetime="2018-07-26T09:57:29+08:00">2018-07-26 09:57:29</time>
                </span>
                <span class="byline"> by
                    <span class="author vcard">
                        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>
                        <a class="url fn n" href="../author/96qbhy">
                            96qbhy
                        </a>
                    </span>
                </span>
                <span class="article-views">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-eye"></i>
                    2093 Views
                </span>
                <span class="comments-link">
                    <i class="glyphicon ipt-icon-bubbles2"></i>
                    <a href="../post/9469.html#comments">
                        0 Comments
                    </a>
                </span>
            </div><!-- .entry-meta -->
        </header><!-- .entry-header -->

        <div class="clearfix"></div>

                                                                                                    <div class="pull-left kb-thumb-medium hidden-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9469.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="256" height="128" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-256x128.jpg" class="img-rounded wp-post-image" alt=""/>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                                                                                <div class="kb-thumb-large visible-xs">
                        <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9469.html" class="thumbnail">
                            <img width="640" height="200" src="https://static.laravelacademy.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/laravel-640x200.jpg" class="img wp-post-image" alt="" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                                    
        <div class="entry entry-excerpt">
            <p>什么是 jwt ?
JWT 全称叫 JSON Web Token, 是一个非常轻巧的规范。这个规范允许我们使用 JWT 在用户和服务器之间传递安全可靠的信息。

jwt 使用场景
jwt 用图广泛，例如授权、鉴权等。具体一点的话，假如我们有一个 A 用户想要邀请某用户进入自己的群组，此时 A 用户需要生成一条邀请链接，链接内容大致如下: https://host/group/{group...</p>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <footer class="entry-meta">
            <p class="visible-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9469.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></i> 阅读全文
                </a>
            </p>
            <p class="pull-right hidden-xs">
                <a rel="bookmark" href="../post/9469.html" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-link"></i> 阅读全文
                </a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted hidden-xs meta-data">
                <span class="cat-links">
					<i class="glyphicon glyphicon-folder-open"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    分类：
                    <a href="../resources/underlying" rel="category tag">
                        基础技术
                    </a>
                </span>

                <span class="tags-links">
					<i class="glyphicon glyphicon-tags"></i>
                    标签：
                                            <a href="Laravel" rel="tag">Laravel</a>
                                                    ,
                                                                    <a href="JWT" rel="tag">JWT</a>
                                                    ,
                                                                    <a href="https://laravelacademy.org/tags/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8" rel="tag">安全</a>
                                                    ,
                                                                    <a href="https://laravelacademy.org/tags/%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83" rel="tag">授权</a>
